ZH: 我今天穿一件蓝色的衣服。
EN: I am wearing a blue shirt today.

ZH: 昨天我买了一条新的裙子。
EN: I bought a new dress yesterday.

ZH: 我的衣柜里有很多不常穿的衣服。
EN: There are many clothes in my closet that I rarely wear.

ZH: 我最喜欢的衣服是一件白色的T恤。
EN: My favorite piece of clothing is a white t-shirt.

ZH: 这件衬衫我穿了很多次了。
EN: I have worn this shirt many times.

ZH: 女孩们喜欢穿漂亮的裙子。
EN: Girls like to wear pretty dresses.

ZH: 他买了一条高质量的皮带。
EN: He bought a high-quality belt.

ZH: 她的衣服都很时尚。
EN: Her clothes are all very stylish.

ZH: 这件外套非常暖和。
EN: This coat is very warm.

ZH: 他的衬衫是一种独特的花纹。
EN: His shirt has a unique pattern.

ZH: 她很讨厌穿连衣裙。
EN: She hates wearing dresses.

ZH: 这种材质的衣服很舒服。
EN: Clothes made of this material are very comfortable.

ZH: 我很忙，没有时间买新衣服。
EN: I am busy and don't have time to buy new clothes.

ZH: 她的衬衣颜色很适合她的皮肤。
EN: The color of her shirt suits her skin tone very well.

ZH: 我需要买一双新的运动鞋。
EN: I need to buy a new pair of sneakers.

ZH: 她擅长设计自己的服装。
EN: She is good at designing her own clothes.

ZH: 这件夹克是我最喜欢的一件。
EN: This jacket is my favorite.

ZH: 他的西装很昂贵。
EN: His suit is very expensive.

ZH: 我希望明天是个晴天，可以穿上我的新裙子。
EN: I hope tomorrow is a sunny day so I can wear my new dress.

ZH: 我要买一条新的泳衣。
EN: I need to buy a new swimsuit.
